	abstract = {The standard procedure to count birds is a manual one. However a manual
bird count is a time consuming and cumbersome process, requiring several
people going from nest to nest counting the birds and the clutches. High
resolution imagery, generated with a {UAS} (Unmanned Aircraft System)
offer an interesting alternative. Experiences and results of {UAS} surveys
